Package Implementation

Class Store

java.lang.Object
Implementation.DataManager
Implementation.Inventory
Implementation.Store
public class Store extends Inventory
The Store class extends Inventory and provides methods to manage a player's store inventory and pricing data. It allows retrieving and updating the price of items in the store based on the player ID and item ID.
